linda ronstadt 's first # 1 album you 're no good , the # 1 smash from this album is probably what made the album a # 1 smash . there was only one other top 20 hit , a cover of the everly brothers ' when will i be loved . yng came to the attention of van halen around 1978 and the band decided to cover the tune . the other songs are good . linda ronstadt 's asylum records labelmate andrew gold plays guitar and sings background on yng .